    "By identifying these concepts, the TIP method improves explanation quality by effectively generating implicit knowledge that aligns with both the nonsensical concepts and the context of the statement.",
    "This deeper understanding enables Llama 2 70B to generate explanations that are more detailed and better aligned with human reasoning.In the last two cases, generated by OPT 1.3B, the limitations of smaller models become more evident with the standard prompts.",
    "Here, the explanations generated by standard prompts are more simplistic and completely fail to address the commonsense contradiction.",
    "However, when integrated with the TIP framework, OPT 1.3B demonstrates significant improvements in explanation generation.",
    "By incorporating the implicit knowledge derived from the nonsensical concepts, the TIP method enables OPT 1.3B to transform its previously entirely incorrect explanations into accurate and contextually appropriate ones."
